data.description: Looking for a move-in home home with a country setting and NO HOA. It's stunning one acre lot offers a serene and picturesque setting, perfect for those seeking a tranquil escape surrounded by natural beauty. House offers a wood burning fireplace in the living room, bathroom vanities finished with granite, large tiled master shower, eat-in kitchen with a brand new stove, heated and cooled sunroom addition, 1-car garage with additional covered parking, storage shed and so much more. Following items to remain with the property: Hot tub, front yard swing, microwave
